{"tid":1543403,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"暗黑兵法","createTime":"2019-09-05T07:25:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T07:57:05.000Z","uid":151338,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e835d2edd1396cf765dc83cb72c8ff295ef70f02","tid":1543403,"uid":151338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:25:13.000Z","msg":"其實有啲暗黑兵法諗左出黎好耐<br />\n不過之前講出黎唔任好啱時候<br />\n<br />\n依家見情況升級哂<br />\n想分響下<br />\n<br />\n依家畜生無委任證 做任何野又唔需要理由<br />\n姦淫擄掠乜7都得<br />\n又無處不在<br />\n有無勇武諗過 搵番件差唔多既衫同棍 <br />\n去啲起左底既黑/藍絲（例如：火車站做9義士果個）<br />\n醒佢地一個「畜生全套」<br />\n一黎比佢地試下畜生們既偉大<br />\n二黎佢班友陷害唔少義士<br />\n三黎減低畜生支持數<br />\n四黎打full gear 9 唔夠打姐，打黑ok la 掛<br />\n<br />\n前提係目標要正確<br />\n最忌點錯相<br />\n呢樣就要老豆搵仔幫幫手<br />\n<br />\n當然<br />\n分享姐<br />\n講到明暗黑兵法<br />\n預左唔會個個受<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">若我們接受了政府的條件<br />\n我們已死去的朋友是不會原諒我們的</span></span>"},{"pid":"ed1cf8c7887d5f8630ed5caa94bcc08790880b77","tid":1543403,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:25:27.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5EAUpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5EAUpQ.jpg&h=30bf1600&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUE1PYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUUE1PYa.jpg&h=d8331036&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1sNZBDb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1sNZBDb.jpg&h=ace5c24e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8KM7Lwx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8KM7Lwx.